s, or synthesize the full report early. Return only the iteration completion report."},"output":"<task id=\"ses_086ce5b08ffePP4gi0KGk1WIRN\" state=\"completed\">\n<task_result>\n## Iteration 2 Complete\n\n**Focus**: system-spec-kit SQLite, FTS, embeddings, incremental ingestion, mutations, and query fusion lifecycle  \n**Findings**: 7 findings (7 new, 0 partially new, 0 redundant)  \n**newInfoRatio**: 1.00  \n**Questions answered**: none fully; Q2 and Q3 materially advanced  \n**Questions remaining**: 5  \n**Edge cases**: ambiguous `mcp_server`/`mcp-server` path spelling resolved from repository evidence  \n**Recommended next focus**: Define the normalized style schema and canonical multi-artifact retrieval-document/hash contract.\n\n**Files written**:\n- `research/lineages/sol/iterations/iteration-002.md`\n- `research/lineages/sol/deep-research-state.jsonl` — appended exactly one iteration record\n- `research/lineages/sol/deltas/iter-002.jsonl`\n- `research/lineages/sol/research.md` — progressively updated\n\n**Verification**:\n- Iteration file exists: yes\n- JSONL iteration append count: 1\n- State/delta canonical records equivalent: yes\n- Findings citations complete: yes\n- Packet boundary respected: yes\n- Reducer-owned files untouched: yes\n- Route proof fields valid: yes\n\n**Status**: complete\n</task_result>\n</task>","metadata":{"parentSessionId":"ses_086d7cfc0ffe217XO92sKCjWRm","sessionId":"ses_086ce5b08ffePP4gi0KGk1WIRN","model":{"modelID":"gpt-5.6-sol-fast","providerID":"openai"},"truncated":false},"title":"Research memory database","time":{"start":1784444724475,"end":1784445022632}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_091bea24c01f4e97016a5c772c2ee081919bf38e93cb39d447"}},"id":"prt_f7931849f0012TIqgdYJv43ewr","sessionID":"ses_086d7cfc0ffe217XO92sKCjWRm","messageID":"msg_f7931747e001jFoIg5b5GviL06"}}
