\",\"summary\":\"Constraints reject duplicate locators and invalid tombstones; partial indexes and external-content FTS triggers are viable.\",\"sources\":[\"command: in-memory SQLite pressure test\",\".opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp-server/lib/search/vector-index-schema.ts:399-432\"]}\n{\"type\":\"finding\",\"id\":\"I003-F7\",\"summary\":\"Q2 is answered with a concrete normalized schema and index contract; Q3 remains for transaction-state-machine research.\",\"sources\":[\"iteration-003.md:Findings\",\"iteration-003.md:Recommended Next Focus\"]}","truncated":false,"loaded":[],"display":{"type":"file","path":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/012-style-database-and-interface-commands/001-research-style-database/research/lineages/sol/deltas/iter-003.jsonl","text":"{\"type\":\"iteration\",\"iteration\":3,\"mode\":\"research\",\"target_agent\":\"deep-research\",\"agent_definition_loaded\":true,\"resolved_route\":\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\",\"run\":3,\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"Define and pressure-test the normalized style schema, constraints, indexes, deterministic retrieval document, and canonical aggregate hash against current manifest fields and multi-artifact inputs.\",\"findingsCount\":7,\"newInfoRatio\":1.0,\"noveltyJustification\":\"7 of 7 findings were fully new concrete schema, mapping, hashing, document, or pressure-test results relative to iterations 1-2.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"Q2\",\"Q3\",\"Q4\",\"Q5\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"Q2\"],\"ruledOut\":[\"One JSON blob per style\",\"Hashing only DESIGN.md\",\"Embedding the complete six-file aggregate\",\"Storing derivable manifest values as independent authority\"],\"focusTrack\":\"normalized-schema\",\"edgeCase\":\"ambiguous-input\",\"toolsUsed\":[\"Read\",\"Glob\",\"Bash\",\"ApplyPatch\"],\"sourcesQueried\":[\".opencode/skills/sk-design/styles/_engine/manifest.mjs\",\".opencode/skills/sk-design/styles/_engine