ty gates pass.\",\"sources\":[\".opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp-server/handlers/memory-index.ts:296-310\",\".opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp-server/handlers/memory-index.ts:1013-1079\"]}\n6: {\"type\":\"finding\",\"id\":\"I004-F5\",\"summary\":\"Publish immutable corpus generation and current pointer in the same transaction as style changes; readers bind one snapshot.\",\"sources\":[\".opencode/skills/sk-design/styles/_engine/manifest.mjs:694-712\",\".opencode/skills/sk-design/styles/_engine/style-library.mjs:119-173\"]}\n7: {\"type\":\"finding\",\"id\":\"I004-F6\",\"summary\":\"Full rebuild uses a verified, WAL-checkpointed staged database/shard and an atomic switch that preserves concurrent old-generation readers.\",\"sources\":[\".opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp-server/lib/embedders/reindex.ts:484-530\",\".opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp-server/lib/embedders/reindex.ts:586-705\"]}\n8: {\"type\":\"finding\",\"id\":\"I004-F7\",\"summary\":\"Durable transaction, queue, and staging evidence makes every crash point resumable without claiming uncommitted success.\",\"sources\":[\".opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp-server/lib/storage/ports/contention-policy.ts:206-233\",\".opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp-server/lib/embedders/reindex.ts:764-780\"]}\n9: {\"type\":\"finding\",\"id\":\"I004-F8\",\"summary\":\"Retain the prior generation so rollback is a guarded pointer reversal before any checkpoint-level restoration.\",\"sources\":[\".opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp-server/lib/embedders/reindex.ts:654-763\",\".opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp-server/lib/storage/checkpoints.ts:2652-2666\"]}\n\n(End of file - total 9 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"{\"type\":\"iteration\",\"iteration\":4,\"mode\":\"research\",\"target_agent\":\"deep-research\",\"agent_definition_loaded\":true,\"resolved_route\":\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\",\"run\":4,\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"Design the crash-safe incremental s