{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1784446288347,"sessionID":"ses_086d7cfc0ffe217XO92sKCjWRm","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_U08rxrwsPZx204zFsWsrUioT","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Research retrieval API","subagent_type":"deep-research","command":"/deep:research:auto","prompt":"Execute exactly ONE deep-research LEAF iteration, iteration 5 of 10, session fanout-sol-1784444104016-7oed3t.\n\nFocus: Specify and pressure-test the generation-consistent structured plus semantic retrieval API wired into `styles/_engine`. Preserve current eligibility/rights and CLI/card/hydration contracts while replacing read-time corpus walking with persistent FTS5 and embeddings. Define request/response fields, hard filters, lexical/vector fusion, score attribution, generation pinning, hydration tokens, pagination/top-k, deterministic fallbacks when vectors/FTS are unavailable or stale, and compatibility adapter boundaries. Ground in current engine and system-spec-kit hybrid search code.\n\nRead state first from the lineage packet. Write only iteration 005, one canonical state append, delta 005, and optional progressive research.md inside `research/lineages/sol`. Do not edit reducer-owned files or any path outside the lineage. No subagents. Exact file:line citations and canonical route proof required. Convergence telemetry must not stop this forced 10-iteration run. Return only the iteration completion report."},"output":"<task id=\"ses_086bc1f7bffeWqE1Z8LLW7NHxe\" state=\"completed\">\n<task_result>\n## Iteration 5 Complete\n\n**Focus**: Generation-consistent structured and semantic retrieval API for `styles/_engine`\n**Findings**: 9 findings (9 new, 0 partially new, 0 redundant)\n**newInfoRatio**: 1.0\n**Questions answered**: Q4\n**Questions remaining**: 2\n**Edge cases**: none\n**Recommended next focus**: Q5 source-of-truth, migration, dual-read verification, cutover, rollback, and repair stages\n\n**Files written**:\n- `research/lineages/sol/iterations/iteration-005.md`\n- `research/lineages/sol/deep-research-state.jsonl` (one canonical iteration record appended)\n- `research/lineages/sol/deltas/iter-005.jsonl`\n- `research/lineages/sol/research.md` (progressive synthesis updated)\n\n**Verification**:\n- Iteration file exists: yes\n- JSONL iteration append count: 1\n- Delta canonical record matches state record: yes\n- Findings citations complete: yes\n- Canonical route proof recorded: yes\n- Packet boundary respected: yes\n- Reducer-owned files untouched: yes\n- No sub-agents dispatched: yes\n- Forced 10-iteration policy preserved: yes\n\n**Status**: complete\n</task_result>\n</task>","metadata":{"parentSessionId":"ses_086d7cfc0ffe217XO92sKCjWRm","sessionId":"ses_086bc1f7bffeWqE1Z8LLW7NHxe","model":{"modelID":"gpt-5.6-sol-fast","providerID":"openai"},"truncated":false},"title":"Research retrieval API","time":{"start":1784445919366,"end":1784446288341}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0af7f8418d45deb5016a5c7bdac75c81918a3c44ee987480f7"}},"id":"prt_f7943cecf0018MZO3eNK36fOag","sessionID":"ses_086d7cfc0ffe217XO92sKCjWRm","messageID":"msg_f7943ba4d001SaWRpJMKpWmtCV"}}
